name: autumn sprinkled with fairy dust
description: A hypercolorized photograph of Vltava river taken in Vysehrad, Prague on autumn of 2019 as one of my contributions for #OBJKT4OBJKT and #NFTsForAll #WorldArtDay2021 . My chosen theme is "Environment". Nature is the most wonderful work of art and my biggest inspiration to create. As humans, we are capable of making great things but we will never be able to outdo what the magic of life in our planet provides for us.
